location.fullValue: Winston Plan, Quarry Hills - D.R. Horton

data.description: Beautiful 2 story 4 bedroom home in Graham's Laurelton Village. Conveniently located within a few minutes to I40/85 for easy commute to RDU, Chapel Hill, or Triad. This home features two master suites, one up and one on the main floor. Upstairs master with 2 closets, duel vanities, soaking tub and walk-in shower. Stunning two story open foyer. Open bonus area for 2nd living area on the second floor. Kitchen with large bar, granite tops and all of the stainless appliances, including refrigerator to convey. Backyard with covered patio with woods behind to give you a feeling of privacy. 10x16 storage building.
